ction/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Profile-da28c11.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=2222%2C1481 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Profile-da28c11.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Profile-da28c11.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Profile-da28c11.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Profile-da28c11.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=2222%2C1481 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Profile-da28c11.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Side view of helmet with flow visualisation\" title=\"Side view of helmet with flow visualisation\" src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Profile-da28c11.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\"></picture></div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> The design of S-Works Prevail II Vent is focused on maximum cooling.</span></figcaption><p><span><i>Specialized</i></span></p></div><p>While Specialized’s Evade helmet is all about reducing drag, the S-Works Prevail II Vent is focused on increasing airflow over the rider’s head, a particular concern for hot weather riding.</p><p>Specialized says the new lid offers a 20 per cent increase in vented area and moves air across the head 18 per cent faster than the standard Prevail II, making it the coolest helmet the brand has ever made.</p><p>This was achieved by the removal of seven foam ‘bridges’ across the central channel of the helmet.</p><div><picture><source 