/images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Vent_Detail-b6ab0c0.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=407%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Vent_Detail-b6ab0c0.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=815%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Vent_Detail-b6ab0c0.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1223%2C815 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Vent_Detail-b6ab0c0.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1631%2C1087 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Vent_Detail-b6ab0c0.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Vent_Detail-b6ab0c0.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Vent_Detail-b6ab0c0.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Vent_Detail-b6ab0c0.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=2222%2C1481 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Vent_Detail-b6ab0c0.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Vent_Detail-b6ab0c0.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Vent_Detail-b6ab0c0.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Vent_Detail-b6ab0c0.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=2222%2C1481 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Vent_Detail-b6ab0c0.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Centre channel of helmet with thin ropes spanning gap\" title=\"Centre channel of helmet with thin ropes spanning gap\" src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Vent_Detail-b6ab0c0.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\"></picture></div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> Spun Aramid ‘ropes’ replace foam bridges for maximum airflow.</span></figcaption><p><span><i>Specialized</i></span></p></div><p>These have been replaced by far more slender “robotically spun Aramid ropes” giving the appearance of an almost completely open channel down the middle of the helmet.</p><p>Like the existing Prevail II, the Prevail II Vent uses MIPS SL safety tech to reduce the effects of rotational forces on the wearer’s head and brain, a system that claims to offer 10 to 15mm of rotation in every direction.</p><p>For the new model, Specialized has used a redesigned MIPS pad kit which aims to be more breathable thanks to a perforated ripstop backing. The new Prevail also includes the <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/specialized-angi-crash-sensor-fee/\">ANGi crash detection system</a> as an additional safety measure.</p><p>We haven’t seen the precise score, because it’s not been published yet, but Specialized says the S-Works Prevail II Vent achieved the maximum five-stars in <a href=\"https://helmet.beam.vt.edu/bicycle-helmet-ratings.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Virginia Tech’s Helmet Ratings</a>.</p><div><picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_SD_Worx-733c771.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=299%2C199, https