_SD_Worx-733c771.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1223%2C815 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_SD_Worx-733c771.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1631%2C1087 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_SD_Worx-733c771.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_SD_Worx-733c771.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_SD_Worx-733c771.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_SD_Worx-733c771.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=2222%2C1481 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_SD_Worx-733c771.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_SD_Worx-733c771.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_SD_Worx-733c771.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_SD_Worx-733c771.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=2222%2C1481 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_SD_Worx-733c771.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"SD Worx rider wearing new helmet\" title=\"Chantal van den Broek-Blaak - Team SD Worx - Specialized\" src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_SD_Worx-733c771.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\"></picture></div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> Expect to see Specialized-sponsored pros wearing the new Prevail this season.</span></figcaption><p><span><i>Luc Claessen / Specialized</i></span></p></div><p>The S-Works Prevail II Vent is available now in four colours. Expect to see it worn by pro riders from teams including Deceuninck–Quick-Step, Bora–Hansgrohe, Legion of LA and SD Worx.</p><p>It will be interesting to see which riders opt for the Prevail over the more aero but less vented <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/reviews/helmets/road-cycling-helmets/specialized-s-works-evade-with-angi-review/\">Evade</a>. Conventional wisdom would suggest that aero gains will usually be more important, but it’s easy to imagine that riders faced with a hot day’s racing would favour the extra airflow offered by the Prevail II Vent.</p><div><p><i title=\"Enlarge photo\" data-slide-index=\"1\">Enlarge photo</i></p><div><picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 375px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 425px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 600px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 767px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 991px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Specialized_Prevail_2_Vent_Studio_MATTE-WHT-CHR-37c6c2e.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=960%2C661\" alt=\"White S-Works Prevail II Vent\" height=\"661\" width=\"960\"></picture><div><p><i><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><title>icon / camera</title><g fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M10 12.08a1.6 1.6 0 1 1 0-3.204 1.6 1.6 0 0 1 0 3.204m0-4.457a2.856 2.856 0 0 0 0 5.711 2.856 2.856 0 0 0 0-5.71\" fill=\"#343434\"></path><path d=\"M16.036 13.2